__XfPolkit__
<a href="https://scan.coverity.com/projects/4197">
  <img alt="Coverity Scan Build Status"
       src="https://scan.coverity.com/projects/4197/badge.svg"/>
</a>



XfPolkit is a simple PolicyKit authentication agent for XFCE(http://xfce.org).

For use this you need that the runned program have a polkit directrice so it will call
the polkit provider (this) also pkexec should be installed to do the task.
